4002   // Build 1 << (-CTLZ & (BitWidth-1)).  The negation likely corresponds to a
4003   // single hardware instruction as opposed to BitWidth - CTLZ, where BitWidth
4004   // is an integer constant.  Masking with BitWidth-1 comes free on some
